\pard\f0\fs28  ({\b b}) Subsp. {\b leopoldii} (Parl.) Snogerup, {\i Bot. Not. }{\b 131}: 187 (1978) ({\i J. leopoldii} Parl.): Inflorescence more or less lax. Capsule 4-5 mm, usually obovoid, obtuse. dark or reddish-brown.{\i  Açores, Portugal}.
